<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.ico">
    <title>Leveraged Synergies: Home of BusinessSpew</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
		padding: 0px;
		margin: 0px;
		box-sizing: 0;
        }
        
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        h1 {
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf-8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><text x="50%" y="50%" font-size="4" fill="#fff" text-anchor="middle">%s</text></svg>') center/contain no-repeat;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -moz-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .api-usage {
            background: rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.9);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        pre {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            padding: 15px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            font-family: monospace;
            color: #00ffcc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .examples {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .example {
            background: rgba(52, 108, 189, 0.9);
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .callout {
            background-color: #eef9f5;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: red;
            border: 4px solid crimson;
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 2em;
        }

 	.content {
		padding: none;
	}

        .callout h2 {
            color: red;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

	.byline {
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: small;
		color: rgba(240, 10, 10, 0.5);
	}

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #8899a6;
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>BusinessSpew 🔥</h1>
        <h2>The Corporate Jargon &amp; Business BS Generator</h2>
        <p>Generate authentic business rhetoric, from boardroom speak to technical posturing.</p>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h3>How It Works</h3>
            <p>BusinessSpew combines carefully curated vocabularies with patterned sentence structures to create content that sounds like it comes from a board meeting, quarterly earnings call, or tech conference keynote.</p>
            
            <h3>Key Features</h3>
            <ul style="color: #ecf0f1;">
                <li>Multiple categories: corporate, tech, startup, AI, and more</li>
                <li>Customizable sentence/paragraph count</li>
                <li>Authentic business patterns &amp; structures</li>
                <li>JSON API for programmatic access</li>
                <li>Local testing with Rackup</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

	<div class="callout" title="<%= @topic.capitalize %>">
        <h2 style="font-weight: bold"><%= @title %></h2>
	<p class="byline"><%= @byline %></p>
	<% @paragraphs.each do |paragraph| %>
   	<p><%= paragraph %></p>
	<% end %>
	</div>
   </div>
    
    <footer>
        BusinessSpew <%= app_version %> | Built with ❤️  in memory of Wilson A. Rogers |
        <a href="https://fly.io" style="color: #3498db;">Deployed on Fly.io</a> |
        <a href="https://digitalocean.com" style="color: #ff6b19;">Powered by DigitalOcean</a>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

